dc_title_s: Digital Aerial Imagery: Milwaukee County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: The dataset consists of 3-inch resolution, color tiled orthogonal imagery produced from nadir images captured by Pictometry International for Milwaukee County in Wisconsin. Automatic aerial triangulation (AAT) was performed. The triangulated frames were rectified to a LiDAR derived DEM. Mosaicking was performed using an automatic seaming algorithm and manually edited to eliminate seams through elevated features where possible.
